POST   /api/posts/create           - Create new post
GET    /api/posts/feed             - Get all posts (feed)
POST   /api/posts/:postId/like     - Like/unlike post
POST   /api/posts/:postId/comment  - Add comment
DELETE /api/posts/:postId/comment/:commentId - Delete comment
PUT    /api/posts/:postId/comment/:commentId - Edit comment
POST   /api/posts/follow/:targetUserId - Follow/unfollow user
GET    /api/posts/user/info        - Get current user info